<p>Here is what i have planned.</p>

<h2 id="how-to-get-things-done">How to get things done?</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Work in sprint of 30 min + 3 minutes break. ( No distractions+ no phone calls+ no messaging) Do all those in this 3 min break.</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="how-many-of-these-sprints">How many of these sprints?</h2>

<ul>
  <li>16 of them in a 9 hours office time. with 18 breaks in between.
Be religious about the count.</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="when-to-plan-a-day-and-how-to-plan">When to plan a day and how to plan?</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Plan one night before the day and also give priorities to new issues or request from Bitbucket, Github.</li>
</ul>

